# arvo-numeric-contracts

Numeric-op trait contracts: `Abs`, `Recip`, `Sqrt`, `TotalOrd`,
`FromConstant`, the `Predicate` family. All `pub const trait`.
Default impl bodies live in the `arvo` facade; concrete impls bind to
`Bits<N, S>`, `UFixed<I, F, S>`, and `IFixed<I, F, S>` downstream.
`#![no_std]`, no alloc.
